-- Temasek in talks to buy stake in Li Ka-shing's Watson - WSJ
-- By Supriya Kurane in Bangalore
-- Thu Mar 20, 2014 11:57PM EDT
-- None



March 20 (Reuters) - Singapore state investor Temasek Holdings [TEM.UL] is in advanced talks to buy a stake in Li Ka-shing's A.S. Watson Co, the Wall Street Journal reported.

